{
  "stem": "16106.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And all the boys were-- were standing around her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they became such, such music lovers!",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She was a very good pianist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She was very lucky girl.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Her father lived in South Africa.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the family lived in Libau.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And once a year, or once-- he came to visit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And when he came to visit, of course they could have-- Marcie could have, or Hilda could have, anything she wanted.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I, I said anything she wanted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We'd say, now you two girls go to the movies.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That was a big deal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Not only go to the movies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Here is money, go and get yourself a cheesecake.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So we can go to the movies and a cheesecake.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But my parents would never.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They would say either the movie or a cheesecake.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So having a father in South Africa was extremely romantic and very, very good.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that besides, she got out with the last ship of Europe.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[BACKROUND NOISE] She and her family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And to South Africa, and they were saved.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How would you spend your free time with friends?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My free time, be on the bike.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Bikes, bicycling.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Biking about the town and biking out of the town to [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Banadan, ?] to the woods, collecting mushrooms.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The woods are full of mushrooms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had chanterelle no end.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you know chanterelles, those little yellow ones?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And berries, blueberries.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE], little wild strawberries.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we used to, in the evening, go run along the beach and collect amber.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We read a lot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We discussed a lot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we listened to a lot of music.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were quite an intellectual bunch, I would think, looking back to it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was not a-- we didn't do the necking and, and, and all the way and whatever bit what I hear now.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
